### 2. Swim Faster (Better Fitness)
Reduce your time per length while maintaining stroke count.

**Focus on:**
- Kick strength
- Aerobic fitness
- Pace consistency

## The Sweet Spot

The best swimmers optimize BOTH - efficient technique at fast speeds!

